mds-account-primanota
=====================
Tryton module to add a primanota-view.

Install
=======

pip install mds-account-primanota

Requires
========
- Tryton 7.0

Changes
=======

*7.0.9 - 30.01.2024*

- add search for code+name in analytic-line

*7.0.8 - 01.12.2023*

- updt: show parties of origins

*7.0.0 - 01.12.2023*

- compatibility to Tryton 7.0
